{"tid":2377050,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"LP10首賣｜父親逾兩成首期助女兒「容易上車」　等佢日後打工再供","createTime":"2021-01-23T09:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T15:55:46.000Z","uid":101341,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df07dee073efb932336d2a572cf617627e4dfe12","tid":2377050,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"南豐及港鐵（0066）旗下的日出康城LP10，今日（23日）首輪銷售179伙，吸引不少買家到場排隊揀樓。<br />\n<br />\n慈父付逾兩成首期 助女兒上車<br />\n<br />\n居住在觀塘的王小姐便是買家之一，在父親協助下成功入市。王先生稱，一家居住在觀塘區，是次女兒以首置身份，斥800多萬元購入兩房單位自住，他替女兒支付約兩至三成首期，助女兒「容易上車」。<br />\n<br />\n王先生選擇建築期付款方法，認為成交期較長，女兒能在日後出來工作後才供樓。<br />\n<br />\n王先生一家原本亦抽到早前開售的啟德MONACO，但認為LP10的性價比較高，故放棄買入MONACO而選擇LP10。<br />\n<br />\n由於單位作自住，加上王先生認為樓價穩價向上，故不太擔心樓價下跌。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">未返工先買樓</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3d1cd8a7637d76ee057a7da3cc55ab580f1a49","tid":2377050,"uid":43369,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"講就咁講姐<br />\n你估個老豆似你地班窮撚冇錢供咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9024771ece83bbbb6113f9cd95cd64375c7dd43f","tid":2377050,"uid":341649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7e3d1cd8a7637d76ee057a7da3cc55ab580f1a49","tid":2377050,"uid":43369,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"講就咁講姐<br />\n你估個老豆似你地班窮撚冇錢供咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又bin c"},{"pid":"37a1288735f2e0fd00c7079c2bd2767bc666f990","tid":2377050,"uid":195728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}